{"tid":2102521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TikTok Teens Are 'Going to War' Against Trump","createTime":"2020-07-10T13:46:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T14:29:39.000Z","uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a170e5ac4a84a22abdad978d64863c07b5b9323","tid":2102521,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"TikTok Teens Are 'Going to War' Against the Trump Campaign After Republicans Call to Ban the App<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/5865261/tiktok-trump-campaign-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5865261%2Ftiktok-trump-campaign-app%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=1a06a739\" target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5865261/tiktok-trump-campaign-app/</a><br />\n<br />\n無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e50083177091242e8fa3545b29f82a2e4ceda09","tid":2102521,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"The TikTok-tivists are at it again.<br />\n<br />\nThousands of users of the popular video app flocked to the Apple App Store in the last few days to flood U.S. President Donald Trump&rsquo;s 2020 campaign app with negative reviews. On Wednesday alone 700 negative reviews were left on the Official Trump 2020 app and 26 positive ones, according to tracking firm Sensor Tower.<br />\n<br />\nTikTok fans are retaliating for Trump&rsquo;s threats of banning the app, which is owned by China&rsquo;s Bytedance Ltd. and is hugely popular in the U.S., especially among teens. The thought of taking away a key social and entertainment hub in the midst of the Covid-19 pandemic has led to outrage.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;For Gen Z and Millennials, TikTok is our clubhouse and Trump threatened it,&rdquo; said Yori Blacc, a 19-year-old TikTok user in California who joined in the app protest. &ldquo;If you&rsquo;re going to mess with us, we will mess with you.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"63fcf4e7f48a524913b621c1c6a014abd82c8b2c","tid":2102521,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T13:51:02.000Z","msg":"This<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iP6XpLQM2Cs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiP6XpLQM2Cs&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=2ea0e8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iP6XpLQM2Cs</a>"},{"pid":"7ccaa5c5cb26730cdb2aecf90dc93ddff7bfcaff","tid":2102521,"uid":3357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係死廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcaf500fe2af1d8c169ed1483c7b9221ffa139f","tid":2102521,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7ccaa5c5cb26730cdb2aecf90dc93ddff7bfcaff","tid":2102521,"uid":3357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲真係死廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"Tiktok d片好撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n花長時間用真係廢青黎"},{"pid":"42a172794112529e3722bb4378344b90f74a9bd9","tid":2102521,"uid":50124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:25:47.000Z","msg":"Ninja今朝話刪左TikTok,應該帶動到佢既fans一齊刪"},{"pid":"39f4daf40fcbf1ecdaf8843288c6d9428ed07b55","tid":2102521,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"話左成個hollyw